div.h2: How skip connections preserve gradient flow through deep transformer stacks

ul.li: Gradient can flow directly through +1 term
Prevents vanishing gradients in deep stacks (100+ layers)
Green animated path = Gradient highway (1.0 identity)
Gray dashed path = Gradient through sublayer (may vanish)
The residual path guarantees gradient magnitude 1.0

div.p: Gradient: L/layer After 12 layers: ~0.001 Result: Vanishing
Gradient: (I + L/layer) After 12 layers: ~12.0 Result: Stable
